one en Rusia junto a Damien Hirst\" 2013-12-30]\n* [http://www.eldia.com.bo/mobile.php?cat=356&pla=7&id_articulo=135212 \"Sonia Falcone en obras de exportaci\u00f3n\" 2013-12-30]\n* [http://www.french-riviera-tendances.org/index.php?option=com_phocagallery&view=category&id=938:vernissage-de-l-exposition-de-damien-hirst-et-sonia-falcone-societe-generale-monaco-le-9-janvier-2014 \"Vernissage de l'exposition de Damien Hirst et Sonia Falcone\" 2014-01-09]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20140608100756/http://arte.elpais.com.uy/lanzamiento-de-la-bienal-de-montevideo-2014/#.VWcAujm9YlI \"Lanzamiento de la Bienal de Montevideo\" 2014-01-24]\n* [http://www.royalmonaco.net/article-monaco-arte-vernissage-sonia-falcone-122277127.html \"Monaco arte: Vernissage Sonia Falcone\" 2014-01-27]\n* [http://hoybolivia.com/Especial.php?IdEspecial=11257 \"Sonia Falcone en M\u00f3naco\" 2014-02-11]\n* [http://www.opinion.com.bo/opinion/articulos/2014/0221/noticias.php?id=120557&calificacion=1 \"Arte de boliviana Sonia Falcone recorre europa\" 2014-02-21]\n* [http://eju.tv/2014/04/sonia-falcone-exhibe-su-arte-en-casa-cor-bolivia/ \"Sonia Falcone exhibe su arte en CASA COR, Bolivia\" 2014-04-12]\n* [http://www.eldia.com.bo/mobile.php?cat=356&pla=7&id_articulo=143543 \"El trabajo de Sonia Falcone se exhibe en CASA COR\" 2014-04-22]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20150924085157/http://www.re-title.com/public/newsletters/10_June_14_-_PINTA_LONDON_12-15_June_2014_0.htm \"Pinta London celebrates fifth anniversary\" 2014-06]\n* [http://www.independent.ie/entertainment/theatre-arts/former-miss-bolivia-adds-some-spice-to-art-show-with-potted-version-of-market-30336133.html \"Former Miss Bolivia adds some spice to art show with potted version of market\" 2014-06-07]\n* [http://www.apollo-magazine.com/gallery-pinta-art-fair-2014/ \"Gallery pinta art fair 2014\" 2014-06-08]\n* [https://archive.is/20150701143638/http://www.lostiempos.com/lecturas/artes-plasticas/artes-plasticas/20140608/bolivia-con-falcone-en-la-bienal-de-dublin_257821_564796.html \"Bolivia con Sonia Falcone en la Bienal de Dublin\" 2014-06-08]\n* [http://www.g77bolivia.com/es/cumbre-g77-campos-de-color-de-sonia-falcone-sera-el-centro-de-mesa-de-la-plenaria \"Campos de Color de Sonia Falcone ser\u00e1 el centro de mesa de la plenaria\" 2014-06-09]{{dead link|date=May 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}\n* [http://www.eldiario.net/noticias/2014/2014_06/nt140612/politica.php?n=92&-campos-de-color-se-exhibira-en-la-plenaria \"Campos de Color se exhibir\u00e1 en la plenaria\" 2014-06-12]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20150923193414/http://www.boliviaexterior.com/seccion/1-politica/noticia/84948-Campos-de-Color-se-exhibira-en-la-Plenaria.html \"Campos de Color se exhibir\u00e1 en la plenaria\" 2014-06-12]\n* [http://www.harpersbazaar.co.uk/culture-news/bazaar-art/the-highlights-pinta-london-2014#slide-2 \"The Highlights Pinta London 2014\" 2014-06-12]\n* [http://www.lavanguardia.com/cultura/20140612/54408950518/la-feria-de-arte-latinoamericano-pinta-sube-el-telon-en-londres.html \"La feria de arte latinoamericano Pinta, sube el tel\u00f3n en Londres\" 2014-06-12]\n* [http://www.express.co.uk/pictures/galleries/2087/World-In-Focus-13th-14th-June-Today-s-best-Pictures-from-around-the-globe \"Best pictures from around the globe\" 2014-06-13]\n* [http://www.lahora.com.ec/index.php/noticias/show/1101686021#.VWb-sjm9YlI \"Feria de arte latinoamericano se abre en Londres\" 2014-06-13]\n* [https://archive.is/20150701143652/http://www.lostiempos.com/diario/actualidad/tragaluz/20140613/se-inicia-feria-de-arte-latinoamericano_258475_566376.html \"Se inicia feria de arte latinoamericano\" 2014-06-13]\n* [https://archive.is/20150701143700/http://yucatan.com.mx/imagen/breves-culturales/breves-de-arte-y-cultura-55 \"Breves de Arte y Cultura\" 2014-06-13]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20150923235315/http://www.eldeber.com.bo/bolivia/cita-excusa-llenar-arte-ciudad.html \"La cita fue una excusa para llenar de arte la ciudad\" 2014-06-16]\n* [http://www.opinion.com.bo/opinion/articulos/2014/0619/noticias.php?id=130953 \"2014 consolida a Sonia Falcone\" 2014-06-19]\n* [http://www.jornadanet.com/n.php?a=105226-1%20( \"Campos de Color - de Sonia Falcone, hace historia en el G77\" 2014-06-20]\n* [http://chq.ie/alternative-views/ \"Alternative views at the Biennial\" 2014-06-23]\n* [http://eju.tv/2014/09/sonia-falcone-y-sus-voces-doradas/ \"Sonia Falcone y sus Voces Doradas\" 2014-09-27]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20160304211720/http://www.minculturas.gob.bo/index.php/prensa/noticias/969-culturas-entrego-reconocimientos-artisticos-a-gaston-ugalde-y-sonia-falcone \"Culturas entreg\u00f3 reconocimientos art\u00edsticos a Gast\u00f3n Ugalde y Sonia Falcone\" 2014-10]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20160304133339/http://www.lostiempos.com/diario/actualidad/tragaluz/20141203/obras-de-dos-bolivianos-en-art-basel-de-miami_283128_623656.html \"Obras de dos bolivianos en Art Basel de Miami\" 2014-12-03]\n* [http://www.blouinartinfo.com/news/story/1066711/at-pinta-a-laid-back-vibe-paired-with-serious-art# \"At pinta a laid back vibe paired with serious art\" 2014-12-05]\n* [https://archive.is/20150701143702/http://elmundo.com.bo/elmundo/noticias/sonia-falcone-expone-artesanias \"Sonia Falcone expone artesan\u00edas\" 2015-04-20]\n* [http://www.paginasiete.bo/cultura/2015/4/29/sonia-falcone-presenta-obra-bienal-venecia-54923.html%20( \"Sonia Falcone presenta su obra en la Bienal de Venecia\" 2015-04-29]{{dead link|date=May 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}\n* [http://www.la-razon.com/la_revista/Artistas-Falcone-Laura-llevan-aymara-Venecia_0_2262373765.html \"Artistas Falcone y Laura llevan el Aymara hasta Venecia\" 2015-04-30]\n* [http://www.eldiario.es/cultura/politicas_culturales/Pan-Belleza-espera-Bienal-Venecia_0_385311804.html \"El pan y la belleza: Lo que nos espera en la Bienal\" 2015-05-7]\n* [http://www.stranieriinitalia.it/nuovi_cittadini-voces_indigenas_alla_biennale_di_venezia_l_anima_dei_popoli_latinoamericani_20169.html \"Voces Indigenas, alla Biennale di Venezia L'anima dei popoli latinoamericani\" 2015-05-08]\n* [https://archive.is/20150701143649/https://fr.news.yahoo.com/photos/cocktail-d%C3%AEner-sonia-falcone-c-slideshow/ \"Cocktal et d\u00eener Sonia Falcone - Que c'est gai, Venise!\" 2015-05]\n* [http://www.gala.fr/l_actu/news_de_stars/sonia_falcone_brille_a_la_56e_biennale_de_venise_343405 \"Sonia Falcone brille \u00e0 la 56e Biennale de Venise\" 2015-05]\n\n=== websites ===\n* [http://www.soniafalcone.com Soniafalcone.com]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110515062544/http://www.soniafalcone.net/ Soniafalcone.net]\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Falcone, Sonia}}\n[[Category:Bolivian artists]]\n[[Category:Bolivian painters]]\n[[Category:Bolivian women painters]]\n[[Category:Bolivian emigrants to the United States]]\n[[Category:1965 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n", "text_old": "{{More citations needed|date=April 2020}}{{Infobox artist\n| name        = Sonia Falcone\n| image       = \n| caption     = \n| birth_name   = Sonia Montero\n| birth_date   = {{birth date|1965|03|27|mf=y}}\n| birth_place  = [[Santa Cruz de la Sierra]], Bolivia\n| nationality = Bolivian\n| field       = Painting and Installation\n}}\n\n'''Sonia Falcone''', born March 27, 1965 in [[Santa Cruz de la Sierra]], [[Bolivia]],<ref name=\":5\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.lavozdelsandinismo.com/cultura/2013-08-08/pintora-boliviana-sonia-falcone-presenta-atractiva-obra-en-bienal-de-venecia/|title=Pintora boliviana Sonia Falcone presenta atractiva obra en Bienal de Venecia - LVDS|date=2013-08-08|website=La Voz del Sandinismo|language=es|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.artealdia.com/Reviews|title=Reviews - Arte Al D\u00eda|website=www.artealdia.com|access-date=2020-04-09}}</ref> is a Bolivian artist known for her painting and installation work. She currently resides in Mexico and is a naturalized Mexican citizen.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elsoldemexico.com.mx/circulos/sonia-falcone-piezas-de-exhibicion-reciclaje-3370955.html|title=Sonia Falcone se une a la preservaci\u00f3n del planeta a trav\u00e9s del reciclaje|last=M\u00e9xico|first=Mildred Estrada {{!}} El sol de|website=El Sol de M\u00e9xico|language=es|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n\n== Early life ==\nAt an early age Falcone moved to the [[United States]] where she began to paint. As a child, she wanted to be a dentist; she attended nursing school but finally chose art as her career. Sonia represented her homeland in Japan with the title of [[Miss Bolivia]] International 1988.<ref name=\":4\">{{Cite web|url=http://eju.tv/2013/07/sonia-montero-maestra-del-estilo/|title=Sonia Montero, maestra del estilo|website=eju.tv|language=es|access-date=2020-04-09}}</ref>  She is an activist for health and education, a supporter and promoter of children's rights, and protector of women who suffered domestic violence.<ref name=\":0\" /><ref name=\":1\" /><ref name=\":3\">{{Cite web|url=https://tendenciaelartedeviajar.com/en/2019/11/on-tendencia-en/ama-foundation-in-the-fight-to-save-the-oceans/|title=AMA foundation in the endeavor to save the oceans|date=2019-11-12|website=Tendencia Magazine - travel, hotels, restaurants in Los Cabos|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref><ref name=\":2\" />\n== Philanthropic work ==\n\nFalcone was invited as a volunteer by the [[Scottsdale, Arizona|Scottsdale]] Center for the Arts Museum ([[Arizona]], [[United States]]) and devoted her time to community projects related to and in support of art: improvement and maintenance of the opera, theatre, and the Museum of the city. As a member of the Board, she promoted the involvement of marginalized Latino communities to arts-related tasks. She is the founder of Essant\u00e9 Corporation (1992-2004),<ref name=\":4\" /> a multinational entity which was established specifically for people seeking better health and greater opportunities in their lives.<ref name=\":4\" /> She is also the founder and president of the AMA Saving the Oceans Foundation<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://tendenciaelartedeviajar.com/en/2019/11/on-tendencia-en/ama-foundation-in-the-fight-to-save-the-oceans/|title=AMA foundation in the endeavor to save the oceans|date=2019-11-12|website=Tendencia Magazine - travel, hotels, restaurants in Los Cabos|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref><ref name=\":1\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.diarioelindependiente.mx/2020/03/museo-de-la-ballena-podria-tener-como-nueva-sede-los-cabos|title=Museo de la Ballena...|last=Yanez|first=Brenda|date=2020-04-13|website=Diario El Independiente|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref>, as well as the Sonia Falcone Foundation.<ref name=\":2\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.20minutos.com.mx/noticia/851033/0/la-escultora-sonia-falcone-y-su-arte-sostenible/|title=La escultora Sonia Falcone y su arte sostenible|date=2020-01-02|website=www.20minutos.com.mx - \u00daltimas Noticias|language=es-MX|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n\n== Artistic career ==\nFalcone exhibited her work in [[La Paz]] (Nota Gallery) in July 2010{{Citation needed|date=April 2020|reason=citation required}} and [[Santa Cruz de la Sierra|Santa Cruz]] (Lorca Gallery) in September 2010{{Citation needed|date=April 2020|reason=citation required}} - [[Bolivia]], in PINTA [[New York City]] (December 2010),<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.revistasexcelencias.com/arte-por-excelencias/editorial-13/ensayo/pinta-ny-en-su-quinto-aniversario-sobre-el-fin-de-toda-iden|title=Pinta NY en su quinto aniversario: Sobre el fin de toda identidad {{!}} Revistas Excelencias|website=www.revistasexcelencias.com|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref> [[Miami International Art Fair]] <ref>[http://mia-artfair.com/press_articles/releases/print/mia_release_features.pdf Press Article in mia-artfair.com] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110821212926/http://mia-artfair.com/press_articles/releases/print/mia_release_features.pdf |date=2011-08-21 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.miaminewtimes.com/arts/best-art-from-miami-international-art-fair-6489236|title=Best Art From Miami International Art Fair|last=McCorquodale|first=Amanda|date=2011-01-14|website=Miami New Times|access-date=2020-04-09}}</ref> (January 2011) and from June 6, in PINTA <ref>[http://www.undo.net/it/mostra/121216 Article in www.undu.net]</ref>[[London]] (June 2011).\n\nIn these exhibitions, Falcone manifests another phase of her personality with her most well-known work, \"Windows of the Soul\",<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://curiator.com/art/sonia-falcone/ventanas-del-alma-windows-of-the-soul|title=Ventanas Del Alma (windows Of The Soul) by Sonia Falcone|website=Curiator|language=en|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref> revealing elements that reflect her life experience. Spirituality is a central element in her work. Her spiritual ideal can be found in all structures, cosmic or individual, organic or inorganic, but achieves its full expression in the human form, shown in her monumental multicolored pieces, with rainbows, snow-capped peaks of the Andes, shadows that banish sunrises, the construction of a world with llamas and fish and where, living the art of war, the sun of justice rose and the drops of blood became art and poetry.\n\nVideo Art Installation, a major piece of this artist, participated in the XVII Bienal de Arte de [[Santa Cruz de la Sierra]], where Sonia was invited to participate.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.my-bolivia.com/best-video-installation-art-at-the-biennale-in-santa-cruz-bolivia-by-sonia-falcone/|title=Best Video Installation Art at the Biennale in Santa Cruz Bolivia by SONIA FALCONE|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-09}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.my-bolivia.com/best-video-installation-art-at-the-biennale-in-santa-cruz-bolivia-by-sonia-falcone/|title=Best Video Installation Art at the Biennale in Santa Cruz Bolivia by SONIA FALCONE|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-09}}</ref>\n\nAt the beginning of the [[3rd millennium|third millennium]], after receiving an [[Honorary degree|honorary doctorate]] from Trinity College of Graduate Studies <ref>[http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Businesswoman-Philanthropist+Sonia+Falcone+to+Receive+Honorary...-a075602619 PR Newswire June 18 2001]</ref> in \"Spirituality and Psychology\", she joined her social and artistic work, viewing art as a tool that could be used not only to understand people's problems, but also to help them think.\n\n\"Passions of the Soul\", one of her most recent works, achieves a rapport between art and game, trying to reach the adult and the child within by creating metaphors that express a philosophy of life.\n\nFalcone's work has appeared in several collectives, mainly in [[Phoenix City Government Convention Center]]\u2013 Civic Plaza, invited by the [[National Hispanic Woman Corporation]].  She has had solo exhibitions at the Museum of Phoenix, [[Calvin Charles Gallery]] in [[Scottsdale, Arizona]],{{Citation needed|date=April 2020|reason=citation required}} and \"The Gallery\" in [[Cabo San Lucas]], [[Mexico]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.oceanblueworld.com/make-it-happen/honoring-the-seas-with-sonia-falcones-ocean-scapes-baja-series-exhibition/|title=Honoring the Seas with Sonia Falcone's Ocean Scapes, Baja Series Exhibition|date=2020-03-05|website=Ocean Blue WORLD|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-09}}</ref>\n\nIn 2013 her work was showcased alongside Damien Hirst's at the Moscow Art Fair by the London, UK gallery Magdalena Gabriel Fine Arts.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.lapatriaenlinea.com/?nota=168064|title=Boliviana Sonia Falcone exhibe su obra en Moscu con Damien Hirst|last=|first=|date=|website=La Patria|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n\nAlso in 2013, Falcone's colorful installation using spices and called ''Campo de Color'' was part of the Latin American Pavilion at the 2013 [[Venice Biennale]].<ref name=\":5\" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/gallery/2013/may/29/venice-biennale-ai-weiwei-best-pictures|title=Venice Biennale: Ai Weiwei, Milla Jovovich and the best of the rest - in pictures|date=2013-05-29|work=The Guardian|access-date=2020-04-09|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077}}</ref> In 2017, that same installation work was included in the [[Nevada Museum of Art]] in Reno, NV group show titled \"Unsettled\", which also travelled to the [[Anchorage Museum]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.adn.com/arts/2018/05/10/anchorage-museums-unsettled-is-a-sensory-exploration-of-the-ever-changing-greater-west/|title=Anchorage Museum\u2019s \u2018Unsettled\u2019 is a sensory exploration of the ever-changing \u2018Greater West\u2019|date=2018-05-11|website=Anchorage Daily News|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-09}}</ref> in Alaska, and California's [[Palm Springs Art Museum]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://lasvegassun.com/news/2017/oct/31/art-exhibit-explores-exploitation-beauty-of-greate/|title=Art exhibit explores exploitation, beauty of 'Greater West' - Las Vegas Sun Newspaper|last=Sonner|first=Scott|last2=Press|first2=Associated|date=2017-10-31|website=lasvegassun.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-09}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nevadaart.org/art/exhibitions/unsettled/|title=Unsettled|website=Nevada Museum of Art|language=en|access-date=2020-04-09}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.palmspringslife.com/art-exhibitions-palm-springs/|title=Art Exhibitions Offer Large-Scale Perspective of the Desert|date=2018-12-10|website=Palm Springs Life|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-09}}</ref>\n\nMore recently, in 2019 her solo exhibition - titled ''Ocean Scapes. Baja Series'' - was hosted by  the Alfredo Ginocchio Gallery in San Jos\u00e9 del Cabo, Mexico.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elsudcaliforniano.com.mx/circulos/inaugurara-sonia-falcone-exposicion-en-los-cabos-4861429.html|title=Inaugurar\u00e1 Sonia Falcone, exposici\u00f3n en Los Cabos|last=Sudcaliforniano|first=Anan\u00ed Arana {{!}} El|website=El Sudcaliforniano|language=es|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n\n== Private life ==\nShe is married to businessman [[Pierre Falcone]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.digitaljournal.com/blog/17040|title=Sonia Falcone's Opening Causes a Sensation in Monaco - Eric Deville - Digital Journal|website=www.digitaljournal.com|access-date=2020-04-09}}</ref> and they have three children: Perrine, Eugenie and Pierre Philippe.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://artjed.com/artists/sonia-falcone/|title=Sonia Falcone : Art JED Gallery|website=artjed.com|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n\n== Selected works ==\n\n* ''Passions of the Soul'' (2010)\n* ''Creation'' (2010)\n* ''Llama'' (2010)\n* ''Video art Installation'' (2010)\n* ''Drops of Blood Installation'' (2010)\n* ''Live Soul Installation'' (2010)\n* ''Blue Water'' (2008)\n* ''Dawn'' (2008)\n* ''Sun of Righteousness'' (2008)\n* ''All eyes on you'' (2011) Mixed media installation \u2013 160x60 cm\n* ''Walking on Eggshells'' (2011) Mixed media installation \u2013 200 aluminum cubes and 300 stainless steel eggs  - Dimensions variable\n* ''Self-portrait I, II, III'' (2011) 3D scanning printed on translucent photographic paper \u2013 76x121 cm\n* ''See no evil, Hear no evil, Speak no evil'' (2011) 3D scanning printed on translucent photographic paper \u2013 76x121 cm\n* ''Vertigo'' (2011)Oil on linen \u2013 180x108 cm\n* ''Vertigo'' (2011) 200x120 cm \u2013 Oil on linen\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n{{External links|section|date=September 2016}}\n\n== External Links ==\n\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.eldiario.net/noticias/2010/2010_11/nt101102/6_01clt.php |title=Sonia Falcone presents her work Windows of the Soul |author= |date=2010-10-02 |work= |publisher= |accessdate=8 June 2011}}\n* [http://www.miaminewtimes.com/arts/best-art-from-miami-international-art-fair-6489236 \"Best Art from Miami International Art Fair\" 2011-01-14]\n* {{cite web |