6711/at-pinta-a-laid-back-vibe-paired-with-serious-art# \"At pinta a laid back vibe paired with serious art\" 2014-12-05]\n* [https://archive.is/20150701143702/http://elmundo.com.bo/elmundo/noticias/sonia-falcone-expone-artesanias \"Sonia Falcone expone artesan\u00edas\" 2015-04-20]\n* [http://www.paginasiete.bo/cultura/2015/4/29/sonia-falcone-presenta-obra-bienal-venecia-54923.html%20( \"Sonia Falcone presenta su obra en la Bienal de Venecia\" 2015-04-29]{{dead link|date=May 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}\n* [http://www.la-razon.com/la_revista/Artistas-Falcone-Laura-llevan-aymara-Venecia_0_2262373765.html \"Artistas Falcone y Laura llevan el Aymara hasta Venecia\" 2015-04-30]\n* [http://www.eldiario.es/cultura/politicas_culturales/Pan-Belleza-espera-Bienal-Venecia_0_385311804.html \"El pan y la belleza: Lo que nos espera en la Bienal\" 2015-05-7]\n* [http://www.stranieriinitalia.it/nuovi_cittadini-voces_indigenas_alla_biennale_di_venezia_l_anima_dei_popoli_latinoamericani_20169.html \"Voces Indigenas, alla Biennale di Venezia L'anima dei popoli latinoamericani\" 2015-05-08]\n* [https://archive.is/20150701143649/https://fr.news.yahoo.com/photos/cocktail-d%C3%AEner-sonia-falcone-c-slideshow/ \"Cocktal et d\u00eener Sonia Falcone - Que c'est gai, Venise!\" 2015-05]\n* [http://www.gala.fr/l_actu/news_de_stars/sonia_falcone_brille_a_la_56e_biennale_de_venise_343405 \"Sonia Falcone brille \u00e0 la 56e Biennale de Venise\" 2015-05]\n\n=== websites ===\n* [http://www.soniafalcone.com Soniafalcone.com]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110515062544/http://www.soniafalcone.net/ Soniafalcone.net]\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Falcone, Sonia}}\n[[Category:Bolivian artists]]\n[[Category:Bolivian painters]]\n[[Category:Bolivian women painters]]\n[[Category:Bolivian emigrants to the United States]]\n[[Category:1965 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n", "name_user": "BoriquaZurdo", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/